response.message:
Thanks for all of your comments! A few follow-ups to your questions:

@Neeharika: Since this is our first event, we'll be learning as we go in person for this round. That said, we'll do our best to bring whatever assets we can to an online audience. 

@Kala J, @Manish P, @CHAN, @krishna, and @Philip: For now, since we're partnering with the City of New York, we're keeping the scope of this event narrow to current New Yorkers. That said, if it's successful, it's possible that we could kick it off in multiple cities.

@Pali Feel free to email info@beyondcoding.io and we'll keep your contact information for when we start planning out future events.
